Package curam.util.ctm.bom.businessobjectidentifier

Contains the interfaces and implemetation classes for business object identifier which assists the business object module infrastructure to uniquely identify a business object in persistent storage using the identifier

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    BusinessObjectIdentifier
    Business object identifier comprises of BusinessObjectType identifier and BusinessObjectKey.
    BusinessObjectIdentifierFactory
    Provides factory methods to create a BusinessObjectIdentifier.
    BusinessObjectKey
    Defines business object key, used by business object modules to uniquely identify an instance of a business object of a particular type.
    BusinessObjectType
    Defines business object type, used by business object modules to specify the type to which business object belongs.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BusinessObjectIdentifierFactoryImpl
    Standard implementation of BusinessObjectIdentifierFactory.
    BusinessObjectIdentifierImpl
    Standard implementation of BusinessObjectIdentifier.
    BusinessObjectKeyImpl
    Standard implementation of BusinessObjectKey.
    BusinessObjectTypeImpl
    Standard implementation of BusinessObjectType.
